00:08:51.599 --> 00:09:00.000
confident, and I'm not surprised. So, I think two things. You can ask it for its level of

00:09:00.000 --> 00:09:06.000
certainty, and I think it's a good thing to do, and it's also good to frame it in uncertainty.

00:09:06.960 --> 00:09:13.039
Tell it, hey, exercise caution. How uncertain are you about this task?

00:09:15.200 --> 00:09:19.280
