00:09:34.320 --> 00:09:41.359
we can correlate the uncertainty scores with actual correct classifications, and it's not

00:09:41.359 --> 00:09:48.479
going to be a perfect correlation, but it is a significant signal, and so you can use it as a

00:09:48.479 --> 00:09:53.200
