00:47:11.439 --> 00:47:19.199
again on a development version, and that way that can also be used. Or I heard about people

00:47:19.199 --> 00:47:24.800
generating random inputs. And I think the term is monkey testing, so you can also apply that

00:47:24.800 --> 00:47:34.479
strategy to try to find those messier edge cases. Awesome. Thank you. It's always hard.

